values: so i stayed home today..i was suppost to do my language shit but idk i decided that its like impossible. so i just hung out with justin all day..he bought me mcdonalds...then i went to work. the pretzletime people are fuckin weird. they all think im older than 17... :/  then i went to d.q. and for like the first time i got hit on while i was tryin to go back to work. bleeeeh. wiggas make me throw up a little, anyways now im home and thats pretty much my day. i have to retake the aims writing tomorrow. im scared. i dont wana go, but eh. welp im out. later tater. chao

Meh...all there are are the fucking weekeneds and even then i have to work or hes grounded for some lame ass reason...theres a few minuets to talk everyday...but mainly just leave messages...no more after school visits...i feel like im slowly being cut off...and fuckin don has to go and say "maybe hes cheating on you"...so i was already thinking of that all day...this shure helps...idk im just spoiled and not use to this lack of...lack of...time, attention, i dont know exactly what...so this is me pouting...or pmsing...who knows anymore im just down right bipolar...
i just dont understand them. i dont want to be here. bye

ya know how somedays everythings just pessimistic and you completley hate you life...you feel shitty as hell then you see that one person and you couldnt be happier. being around nick makes me the most optimistic person in the world. the happiest. the luckiest. even when everything goes wrong, it couldnt be more perfect. its soo mushy gushy. but true. sometimes you just have to look at the whole picture and be greatful for what ya have and who your with. yeah nicks further away for like a year and a half...but if ya think about it. thats nothing. thats a lil tiny dent in a lifetime together, so its not that big of a deal. (or at least as much as i made it seem in my last lj...) its definatly worth it. and even though i regret posting all that in there, at least we got to talk about it so he could know how i felt and its not just bottled up emotions...but still it was harsh...and way overdramatic. i love nick. i dont think that there will ever be a day that i dont. welp peace out.

i hate these nights when i get all confused. and start wondering what i really want and whats right for me...seems like they happen more and more and more now that nicks gone. actually every day. everytime we hang up, er he has to go, i get so frustrated. theres so many things i want to talk about but theres never the right timing..and hes never there. if i love him and still want us to stay together through all this shit, the whole rest of highschool, then why do i get like this? alway pissed of and/or crying. sometimes i think things would be better apart...everytime i think of all the things ive done. and just how hard this is for both of us...is it really worth it all....or is it just because i miss him so much. idk. this is gay. i hate being so young

(bad) anywho. not much is new. today was eventful. school pissed me off alot...stupid. i have alot of stuff to make up and study for. all while goin to work everyday but monday and thursday. then there was that whole fight thing in the parking lot which made me realise alot of things about life. it was depressing. and im extreamly weak-idk just a pussy i guess...and then i worked and that was usual...came home all bitchy and hungry. and apparently everyones been fighting all night. the whole threatining of divorce has resurfaced. but ill belive it when it happens. just all the work and school and drama and buisiness of december has just been getting to me. i actually have a boyfriend to spend it with and ya think i'd be happy to not be alone like always...and dont get me wrong im greatful and all and i love him, just theres always gona be something wrong. and i can only blame myself for having such high expectations or for being optimistic to often. well im goin to catch some shut eye so i can go to Nicks match tomorrow. night.

isnt it crazy how one person can make you do everything that was impossible. prove that 99% probability wrong. how their love and forgivness can help you become everything you never thought that you could. and make everything so perfect. i love you nick. you've saved me so many times in so many ways. i owe you more than i could ever give...i can never stop thanking you. muah.

home. project. bored. lonley. moody. read. thats my day, in short choppy sentences. i count it as artistic, but im a dumb ass so it probley makes no sence...anyways. im just not used to this. never being able to do what i want to...its so strage and sucky. i always figure half days are fun. my rents arnt home, and they dont care if i go out and enjoy it...plus it was my day off... but its differnt with lil chillins runnin around everywhere, and i assume things will be getting pretty busy with everyone with 'the holidays' comming up. its almost the weekend. but i dont care cuz that just means working and a last minuet spanish project. plus im shure nick will be too busy helping move to be able to "go out". so whatever. sometimes im just not happy. now is one of those times. most journal entrys are. i tryed to be a good sister and drive jeremy around. but i just feel gullible and used. tried to explain. but you just dont listen when your at that stage in your life. no matter what. its something hes gona have to get over himself..but it just dosnt seem to me like thats gonna happen. not like things are suppost to be perfect anyways right? out.

So...me and nick are trying to work things out.  whether i want to belive it or not, i know he loves me and is only looking out for the best for me.  i dont know why he gives me so many chances, and i dont think he does either.  it just shows that im really special and mean alot to him. i know that i love him.  and i know that knowing he loves me can help me be shure of that. i know we do get in our stupid little bull crap fights, but who doesnt. its part of a relationship and with some factors cut out of my life i know that we can have the best relationship.

Even though we break up, i know that things will work out and get better because i have so much trust and love in him. Anytime i think of how my future might be, he's always in the picture, and we're always together. i cant imagine myself with anyone else. and im willing to work on things and do whatever it takes to keep us that way.
